{"tid":2128371,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[係香港生活真係好撚難］低薪青年嘆香港閹割夢想「搬去劏房為有喊的角落」","createTime":"2020-07-28T02:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T03:22:05.000Z","uid":315251,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e297c68def40f60e40535d7c0c69fddebf9e4de","tid":2128371,"uid":315251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WOQdpMG11Z8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWOQdpMG11Z8&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=70aa5f04\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WOQdpMG11Z8</a><br />\n<br />\n「以前流行談夢想和興趣，我覺得談錢的人真的很膚淺，為甚麼大人常常談論錢？」年僅24歲的阿霏重提過去對世界的質問，有點腼腆，因為今天的她，稜角已被生活磨蝕，想法不再一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">大家成日話好撚鐘意香港，但問心，我覺得係香港生活好唔開心</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d665059a71968d90942b0727ab7a661a0c79d5b","tid":2128371,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"冇計, 有邊個唔想一出世有幾億身家?<br />\n窮, 比你窮既人大有人在,<br />\n生存先可以談夢想.."},{"pid":"55b1321876ce522b92b037c1b01d60117cfeee08","tid":2128371,"uid":315251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d665059a71968d90942b0727ab7a661a0c79d5b","tid":2128371,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"冇計, 有邊個唔想一出世有幾億身家?<br />\n窮, 比你窮既人大有人在,<br />\n生存先可以談夢想.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T02:48:16.000Z","msg":"先唔講政治環境<br />\n本身香港就係好現實嘅地方<br />\n有錢講生活 冇錢講生存<br />\n講夢想係連登只會被人笑<br />\n賺錢最實際"},{"pid":"256c89097ceec697a8b673c4d37bc77f712d3fcb","tid":2128371,"uid":319138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"淨係讀art 都已經死撚得"},{"pid":"375cdcc6638b6ca5f569d621de02e07ebd416f91","tid":2128371,"uid":315251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"256c89097ceec697a8b673c4d37bc77f712d3fcb","tid":2128371,"uid":319138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020